25 mental health professional that the minor lacks fitness to proceed and there is a
26 substantial likelihood the minor is unable to be remediated within the period of the
27 remediation order, the court may:
28 a. Dismiss the delinquency proceedings and release the minor to the minor's
29 parent, legal guardian, or legal custodian; or
